headline: Loan Growth, Rise in NII to Aid Regions Financial's Q4 Earnings
summary: RF is set to post Q4 results, with loan growth and a rise in NII likely to drive revenues. Yet, high costs are likely to have created a headwind.

headline: Growth in NII, Robust IB Performance to Aid KeyCorp's Q4 Earnings
summary: KEY's Q4 outlook brightens as loan demand lifts NII and strong deal activity fuels investment banking ahead of Jan. 20 earnings.
